<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR3c0004-fr-144c77a1" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Le Livre du Prince Shang</title><editor role="translator">Jean Lévi 1981</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="1"><ab>This work is in the public domain</ab></availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>Le Livre du Prince Shang</title>Paris: Flammarion, 1981</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR3c0004"><title xml:lang="och">商君書</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="fr">French</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2022-09-14T20:22:36.47+09:00</date> by CH</creation><creation resp="#CH">Header modified: <date>2023-10-21T20:28:54.015+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR3c0004-start"><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:41:32.291+09:00">Le duc Xiao tenait conseil</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:41:55.762+09:00">avec ses trois ministres Gongsun Yang, Gan Long et Du Zhi;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:08:59.326+09:00">ils débattaient du changement des moeurs,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:42:57.617+09:00">de l'esprit des institutions,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:43:14.592+09:00">de l'art, enfin, d'user des peuples.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:43:28.466+09:00">Le prince s'exprima en ces termes:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:44:27.342+09:00">"Succéder à ses ancêtres en prenant soin de ses sujets,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:44:54.136+09:00">tel est le rôle du souverain.;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:45:31.421+09:00">établir les lois afin que rayonne la vertu de leur maître,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:45:47.909+09:00">tel le devoir des ministres.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:46:39.606+09:00">Aujourd'hui, je voudrais changer les institutions afin de mieux gouverner mes peuples,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:47:07.089+09:00">et réformer les coutumes pour les mieux instruire.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:47:51.607+09:00">Mais je crains fort que l'empire ne nous blâme.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:50:31.138+09:00">Gongsun Yang:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:50:59.534+09:00">"Je sais d'espérience</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:51:32.488+09:00">que indécision est la mère de l'échec;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:52:37.058+09:00">vous devez, sans balancer d'avantage, réformer les lois</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:53:02.49+09:00">au mépris de l'opinion publique.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:53:44.074+09:00">Les agissements des hommes d'élite</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:54:01.254+09:00">ne sont pas compris du vulgaire;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:54:26.878+09:00">leus desseins</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:55:02.919+09:00">ont toujours provoqué l'indignation de la populace.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:55:18.515+09:00">Does je vous rappeler que</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:55:37.507+09:00">"le sot ne voit pas ce qui est acheve;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:56:13.472+09:00">le sage aper¸oit ce qui n'est pas encore en germe."</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:56:55.038+09:00">On ne peut demander au peuple de collaborer ả notre politique</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:58:16.676+09:00">mais seulement de se r/éjouir avec nos de ses succès.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T19:58:36.734+09:00">Guo Yan ne dit-il pas dans son De la loi:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:00:42.869+09:00">"Qui traite de la vertu suprême</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:00:55.87+09:00">se rit de l'opprobre du vulgaire;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:01:12.314+09:00">qui accomplit  de grands desseins</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:01:25.014+09:00">ne discute pas de ses projets avec la foule."</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:02:53.647+09:00">par la Loi</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:02:28.658+09:00">On protège son peuple;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:03:10.751+09:00">par les Rites</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:03:33.072+09:00">on lui est benefique.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:04:38.226+09:00">C'est pourquoi  un souverain avisé</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:05:06.15+09:00">ne se règle pas sur de vieilles maximes</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:06:02.749+09:00">ni ne respecte d'antiques coutumes pour renforcer son pays et enrichir son people.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:06:29.674+09:00">fit le prince.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:06:44.151+09:00">"Bien".</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:06:51.424+09:00">Gan Long:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:07:01.754+09:00">C'est faux!</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:08:02.593+09:00">Chacun sait</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:08:09.272+09:00">que le prince n'a pas besoin de changer les coutumes pour éduquer  son peuple,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:08:11.148+09:00">ni de modifier les lois pour le gouverner.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:08:37.907+09:00">Il sui les moeurs de ses sujets</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:09:11.201+09:00">et les instruit sans fatique;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:10:16.632+09:00">il conserve leurs lois et la pays est en paix,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:10:26.776+09:00">les foctionnaires efficaces.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:12:06.424+09:00">Songez-y à deux fois avant de boleverser les lois et les institutions eoriuvées de notre royabe Qin,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:12:49.823+09:00">car je crains que l'empire ne vous blâme!</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:13:18.483+09:00">[Songez-y à deux fois]</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:13:51.783+09:00">Gongsun Yang:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:14:27.548+09:00">"Ce ne sont là</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:14:30.89+09:00">que lieux communs.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:15:06.634+09:00">Les médiocres, attacheés aux vieilles recettes,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:15:39.46+09:00">et les lettrés, prisonniers de leurs lectures</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:16:51.211+09:00">peuvent tout juste appliquer les règlements à un poste subalterne;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:17:26.323+09:00">comment distereraient-ils avec nous des grandes affaires qui transcendent l'application des lois?</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:18:28.157+09:00">Les Trois Souverains régnèrent  par des rites diffeérents</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:19:29.705+09:00">et les Cinq Hégémons étendirent  leur domination en s'appuyant sur des lois opposées.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:19:37.386+09:00">Le sage fait la loi,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:19:43.429+09:00">le sot la subit;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:20:14.357+09:00">le premier modifie les rites,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:20:28.676+09:00">le second en est l'esclave.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:21:46.839+09:00">Les confucéens, prisionniers du ces règlements et bridés par la morale,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:22:23.528+09:00">sont incapables de discuter des affaires de l'Etat</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:22:46.916+09:00">et des reformes a entreprendre.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:23:57.892+09:00">Prince, n'ayez point de scrupules!</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:24:20.278+09:00">Du Zhi:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:26:41.864+09:00"/><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:26:30.299+09:00">de même qu'on ne remplace un ustinsile que si l'on est assurée d'une efficacité decuplée.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:26:51.68+09:00">On ne change pas les institutions sanls la certitude d'avantages considérables,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:28:22.713+09:00">Il n'y a rien de mauvais, ce me semble, à s'en tenir aux vieilles coutumes et aux anciennes institutions.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:28:42.264+09:00">Prince, songez-y bien!</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:28:50.462+09:00">Gongsun Yang:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:31:46.492+09:00">"La morale change avec les époques:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:31:58.271+09:00">De quel antique souverain voudriez-vours reprondre les institutions?</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:32:27.446+09:00">Chacun a eu les siennes.:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:35:28.692+09:00"/><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:35:05.547+09:00">Huangdi, Yao et Shun les instituèrent; mais le crime ne retombait pas sur les parents du coupable.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:35:54.415+09:00">Fuxi Shennong gouvernèrent leurs peuples sans recourir aux châtiments;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:36:12.12+09:00">Jusqu'aux rois Wen et Wu,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:37:40.902+09:00">tous les princes établirent les lois</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:37:47.677+09:00">en tenant compte des circonstances.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:38:00.573+09:00">Morale et institutions se conforment à l'esprit du siècle,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:39:54.019+09:00">de meme que les machines sont conçues qui en est fait.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:40:19.093+09:00">Il n'existe pas un principe unique des gouvernement,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:41:28.133+09:00">aussi n'est-ce pas en prenant modèle sur l'Antiquité que l'on renda son pays prospère.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:42:58.219+09:00">Le roi Tang et le roi WWu</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:43:22.148+09:00">ne durent point leur éclat  à leur respect des Ancients</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:43:41.089+09:00">ni les tyrans des Yin et des Xia leur chute</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:44:06.33+09:00">à un changement dans les institutions.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:45:15.346+09:00">Pourquoi  décerner le blâme à ceux qui tounent le does aux anciens rites</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:45:40.53+09:00">et la louange à ceux qui les suivent?</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:46:02.749+09:00">Prince, n'ayez pas de scrupules!</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:46:09.511+09:00">Le duc Xiao:</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:46:15.961+09:00">Bien.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:46:44.851+09:00">Les campagnard s'étonnent de tout</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:47:22.162+09:00">et les lettrés pornés  ergotent sur des evidences.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:47:45.673+09:00">Le sage s'attriste de ce qui réjouit le sot;</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:48:26.12+09:00">S'homme de bien s'afflige de ce qui fait le plaisir du fol.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-16T20:50:33.146+09:00">Ma décision est prise, et je ne me laisserai pas troubler davantage par les avis de lettrés rigides."</seg><seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-24T16:59:10.333+09:00">C'est ainsi que le roi fit promulguer ses dits sur La Mise en Culture des Terres Vierges.</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>